Yan cover for me because of the art show. Top half Defense bottom attack ))

::Tiamat::
Tiamat armor getting nailed as she fold her wings for cover. "Tactics 
Change."

::Lilly::
Lilly takes out 1 of the missiles was she get hit by the second as spirals 
he heat shielding giving some protection. "Whatï¿½s the plan?"

::Liono::
Liono throws a fire rocket at the Emp heading for Key gives her a Thumbs up 
"Wild Cats Grand stream we are pride lets fight like one!" Throws the Fang 
towards Kaiser.

::Key::
Key avoids one blast as the other clips her in her side as it burns "Dark 
Rinoa Duck!" Key fires twin Ice blast at the missiles heading for Dark.

::Dark::
Drops Down as one of the Ice blast freezing a missile in place the other 
hits a blade hanging above his head as it Dark fires taking out the other 
missile.

::Rinoa::
"Dark help with the Grand Stream I'll cover this." Turns her Wild C.A.T.S 
Symbol in a 360 as in her POV she gets an outline of Scthyer locks on and 
Fires 25 Sonic blast at Scthyer

::BlueStinger::
Blue shoot counter blast taking out the 2 missiles.

::Kaiser::
Splits into 2 bots to avoid ships shots as the Fang devours 2 of the Shots 
an returns to Inu  gets hit by the Motormaster shot as he growls in pain.

((Grand Stream Tactics))
::Key::

::Lilly::

::Tiamat::

exploding plasma balls at Motormaster.

::Liono::
